n-hydrogen-plant-in-india-maharashtra-amit-bansal-solar-wind-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20futur%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341870%2Fhygenco-first-green-hydrogen-plant-in-india-maharashtra-amit-bansal-solar-wind-energy%2F%5C%22%3Ee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20countless%20challenges.%20His%20work%20came%20to%20national%20attention%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20programme%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMann%20Ki%20Baat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20praised%20Jagdish%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20a%20recognition%20that%20brought%20both%20joy%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20fulfilment%20to%20the%20humble%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagdish%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20personal%20loss.%20He%20lost%20his%20father%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20his%20life%20that%20left%20a%20deep%20impact.%20The%20tragedy%20could%20have%20crushed%20him%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20it%20became%20the%20catalyst%20for%20a%20life%20built%20around%20resilience%20and%20a%20deep%20connection%20to%20the%20earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20age%20of%2020%2C%20I%20made%20a%20firm%20decision%20to%20honour%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20by%20doing%20something%20meaningful%20with%20the%20land%20he%20had%20left%20behind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20managing%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20farm%2C%20Jagdish%20also%20runs%20a%20small%20ration%20shop%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20another%20way%20he%20contributes%20to%20his%20village%E2%80%99s%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20disappointment%20to%20triumph%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20with%20no%20formal%20training%20but%20an%20unshakeable%20desire%20to%20improve%20his%20circumstances%2C%20Jagdish%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20plant%20fruit%20trees%20on%20his%20land.%20He%20began%20by%20planting%20guava%20an