0teeming%20forest%20with%20vegetable%2C%20fruit%20and%20spice%20trees%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Keyur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Girdhar%20initially%20conceptualised%20the%20space%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F91969%2F7-fabulous-farmstays-india-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimple%20village%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nothing%20too%20dramatic.%20Letting%20us%20in%20on%20those%20days%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sole%20tamarind%20tree%20of%20the%20land%20became%20a%20roof%20over%20our%20heads%20when%20we%20started%20constructing%20a%20home%20on%20this%20untouched%20land.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Keyur%20and%20Nishit%20were%20following%20their%20own%20professional%20trajectories%20while%20watching%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20fondness%20for%20the%20land.%20The%20duo%20wanted%20to%20help%20and%20make%20the%20land%20viable%2C%20more%20abundant.%20But%20neither%20of%20us%20was%20a%20farmer%2C%20notes%20Keyur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20everything%20thereafter%20was%20trial%20and%20error.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20many%20setbacks%20such%20as%20wasted%20seasons%2C%20failed%20crops%2C%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20cyclones%2C%20and%20extreme%20heat.%20Working%20with%20nature%20meant%20surrendering%20to%20its%20whims%20and%20fancies.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282423%2Ftamil-nadu-best-farm-stay-grandma-nature-organic-food-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econscious%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20brothers%20had%20made%20was%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20chemical%20fertilisers%20right%20from%20the%20beginning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%