%20these%20species%20are%20notoriously%20hard%20to%20grow%20outside%20their%20natural%20habitat.%20But%20today%2C%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20home%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20260%20fern%20species%2C%20out%20of%20the%20280%20found%20in%20South%20India%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E110%20of%20the%20140%20known%20Impatiens%20species%20in%20the%20region%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERare%20plants%20like%20Impatiens%20jerdoniae%2C%20an%20epiphytic%20balsam%20that%20had%20almost%20vanished%20in%20the%20wild%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAround%20100%20native%20tree%20species%2C%20restored%20to%20their%20natural%20habitat%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E500%20herbs%2C%20shrubs%2C%20creepers%2C%20climbers%2C%20and%20epiphytes%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20200%20species%20of%20mosses%20and%20liverworts%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nursery%20and%20gardens%20sit%20beneath%20soaring%20rainforest%20trees%2C%20where%20greenhouses%20and%20open%20beds%20offer%20the%20right%20conditions%20for%20fragile%20species%20to%20take%20root%20again.%20Together%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20earned%20Gurukula%20the%20name%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Noah%E2%80%99s%20Ark%20for%20plants%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20living%20collection%20of%20rare%20and%20vanishing%20flora%2C%20kept%20safe%20until%20they%20can%20be%20reintroduced%20to%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Laly%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20guidance%2C%20the%20team%20has%20developed%20low-impact%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F447032%2Fshyam-sunder-jyani-teacher-turned-environmentalist-restored-mining-wasteland-in-rajasthan-with-community-support%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareful%20methods%20of%20restoration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Their%20work%20blends%20traditional%20wisdom%20with%20hands-on%20experimentation.%20There%20are%20no%20fixed%20timelines%20or%20rigid%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20only%2